otherNames: 重回末世当大佬 第三季, 重回末世当大佬 第三1, Chong Hui Mo Shi Dang Da Lao
synopsis: Younger Yang Fan’s younger sister died tragically and was betrayed by his girlfriend. By chance, he was reborn back to before the apocalypse broke out! In the last life, you bullied me, humiliated me, and betrayed me. In this life, you will be reborn! Yang Fan squeezed the super ring in his hand: “Only the strongest can survive, and I am the strongest!”
